{"tid":2495311,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"穗珍拖累(G)I-DLE隊友重新錄歌 徐信愛揭霸凌事件後晒近況","createTime":"2021-04-19T06:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T08:22:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9843ea0172def9d87c776270684fa2dea25129b0","tid":2495311,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2dJH70dk1jzcd-Wyvq4YVlKh-bk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CJELWYAJOJD4JAZNSJXKPZQ564.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2dJH70dk1jzcd-Wyvq4YVlKh-bk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCJELWYAJOJD4JAZNSJXKPZQ564.jpg&h=2400ee92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國女團(G)I-DLE的23歲成員穗珍2月時被爆霸凌同學，事後她承認曾用粗口罵人，但就強調沒有使用過暴力，當中童星出身的徐信愛疑似在網上暗示讀書時曾遭穗珍欺凌，徐信愛上月更開腔指稱讀書的兩年間，一直遭穗珍人身攻擊，引起網民熱議。<br />\n<br />\n穗珍爆出是非後，其所屬的CUBE事務所宣佈她將中斷活動，(G)I-DLE暫時會以5人之姿繼續活動，而今日就有報道指，(G)I-DLE將重新錄製歌曲，以5人體制於月尾推出新歌《Last Dance》。<br />\n<br />\nMV刪減畫面<br />\n據相關人士透露：「《Last Dance》早於2月已完成錄音，以及MV、專輯相等所有拍攝，但由於穗珍爆出爭議，與CUBE事務所進行多方面的討論後，已重新修改及分配5名(G)I-DLE成員的歌詞，再次進行錄製，至於MV，將盡量刪走有穗珍的畫面。」<br />\n<br />\n而徐信愛公開被欺凌一事後，相隔近一個月再更新IG，昨日上載了自己的新相，雖然她戴着口罩，但眼中透着笑意，獲fans大讚可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CoicuUw81I_grEENgmPOAbDL3LY=/802x471/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TQTODIEZHJFYBOKRMH23Y4W7IU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCoicuUw81I_grEENgmPOAbDL3LY%3D%2F802x471%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTQTODIEZHJFYBOKRMH23Y4W7IU.jpg&h=a7600dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k1das0A1bIXueKnFdJOYmnQyA04=/802x1281/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/63B3UUOGIVGFPISP6PIXXDMZUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk1das0A1bIXueKnFdJOYmnQyA04%3D%2F802x1281%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F63B3UUOGIVGFPISP6PIXXDMZUM.jpg&h=e32f12eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5PL9EK2pxjOO4uWR0XCA9-61zic=/802x861/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7HERNRB3DFF47HILHTZXXN4YGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5PL9EK2pxjOO4uWR0XCA9-61zic%3D%2F802x861%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7HERNRB3DFF47HILHTZXXN4YGE.jpg&h=2ff9723b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HtgPSaz_XvKD9YnY8bdyxp5p3dk=/802x1261/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6FDRCBE6SFCBPLVDNU4DVWCEMM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHtgPSaz_XvKD9YnY8bdyxp5p3dk%3D%2F802x1261%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6FDRCBE6SFCBPLVDNU4DVWCEMM.jpg&h=516a5da6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dbd5812a14ab5f19c2e0bdb5e1f54d812ad172b2","tid":2495311,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:05:13.000Z","msg":"可以用Irene 呢編文都可以出"},{"pid":"04ea7b5a8ba767aa293b4a32110c20f1b76ca3c5","tid":2495311,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:08:28.000Z","msg":"條女咁樣衰 抵俾人斯凌"},{"pid":"131ea8a6bd8b1079fa0802c164401eb22266fa19","tid":2495311,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"護琦同舒華唔係各自返左國咩<br />\n4月底返得切去？"},{"pid":"f845bc984706cc015adc191b2266831510233769","tid":2495311,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"